    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1901-09-15T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1901-09-15T00:00:00-05:00" n="119"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d119">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">President <persName type="from">Plaza</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Vice-President of the United States</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Quito, Ecuador</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1901-09-15">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 15, 1901</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The Ecuadorian people and Government join in the legitimate sor row of the Great
                    Republic for the demise of its illustrious President.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Plaza</hi>, <hi rend="italic">President.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
